#

Sweet Chili Sauce

10 min
$3.5
40 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

Thai

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

SauceDippingEasyQuick

Description

A sweet and tangy sauce perfect for dipping or as a glaze!

Ingredients

  • sugar: 1/2 cup
  • water: 1/2 cup
  • rice vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • red chili flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • water (for cornstarch): 2 tablespoons
